comments: Dunn (CHI) moves laterally into Paul (OKC) when going over the pick and affects his SQBR.
Paul (OKC) slightly extends his forearm into Dunn's (CHI) body as he releases from the contact that Dunn initiates, and the contact from Paul is marginal.
Paul (OKC) sets the pick in Markkanen's (CHI) path and absorbs the contact.
Dunn (CHI) makes incidental contact with Paul's (OKC) arm after the release on his jump shot attempt.
Paul (OKC) sets the pick in Markkanen's (CHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Adams (OKC) grabs and holds Satoransky's (CHI) arm and affects his ability to ability to disengage from the screen.
Markkanen (CHI) faces up with Adams (OKC) but does not prevent him from gathering the rebound.
Markkanen (CHI) makes marginal contact with Adams's (OKC) body before Carter Jr. (CHI) makes contact with the ball on the play at the basket.
Replay review of the foul called on Carter Jr. (CHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Dunn (CHI) is not in a legal guarding position when contact occurs with Paul's (OKC) arm on the rip-through.
Paul (OKC) reaches in and makes contact to Dunn's (CHI) arm which affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Paul (OKC) is not in a legal guarding position when he makes contact with Dunn's (CHI) arms that affect Dunn's ability to pass the ball.
Ferguson (OKC) briefly engages LaVine (CHI) with two hands before releasing.
Carter Jr. (CHI) is firming up in a picking position in Ferguson's (OKC) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Ferguson (OKC) holds LaVine's (CHI) arm before he gathers the ball and affects his SQBR during the drive.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes marginal contact with Schroder (OKC) as he disengages from contact after the pick.
Schroder (OKC) is drawn into the air and makes contact contact to LaVine's (CHI) arm which affects his jump shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) makes marginal contact with Schroder (OKC) as he disengages from the contact during the inbound.
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with LaVine (CHI) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Gallinari (OKC) sets the pick in Dunn's (CHI) path and absorbs the contact when contact occurs.
Gallinari (OKC) sets the pick in Dunn's (CHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Markkanen (CHI) makes marginal contact with Paul's (OKC) body before Carter Jr. (CHI) cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Paul (OKC) loses possession of the ball after the block, and regains possession on the ground.
Schroder (OKC) and LaVine (CHI) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Carter Jr. (CHI) wraps Adams (OKC) during the inbound while the pass is in the air.
White (CHI) commits a take foul on Paul (OKC).
Schroder (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position during the shot attempt by LaVine (CHI).
